snippet.title: Tetris26 - Atari 2600 Homebrew
snippet.description:
Developed and released by Colin Hughes way back in 1998, this homebrew imagines what and how would Tetris look and play had it come out on the Atari 2600. The physical cartridge was released later on by Hozer Video Games.

The homebrew game can be downloaded for free here: https://github.com/udibr/tetris26/blob/master/tetris.bin
